<template>
  <v-form>
    <v-row>
      <v-col
        cols="12"
        md="3"

        <v-text-field
          id="firstnameHorizontalIcons"

      </v-col>
      <v-col
        offset-md="3"

          class="mx-2"
        >
          Reset
        </v-btn>

<script>

import {
  mdiAccountOutline,
  mdiCellphone,
  mdiEmailOutline,
  mdiLockOutline,

export default {
  setup() {
    const title = ref('')

    return {
      title,

      // icons
      icons: {
        mdiAccountOutline,
        mdiEmailOutline,
        mdiCellphone,
        mdiLockOutline,
      },
    }
  },
}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
